The story was interesting as well. It her featured a girl who is on a military expedition exploring the universe but she manages to keep in contact with her boyfriend back on earth via text messaging from her cell phone. As she travels further away from earth, it takes longer for her messages to get to him. Eventually, she gets to the point where it takes 8 years for a message to reach him. <br>
I think of this animation not as a stand alone story for fireside discussions on the proliferation of instant digital messaging nor is it another story to pontificate the significance of a long distance relationship or the yearning of human contact in a bleak moment like war.  Rather, this is something that you watch with your art buddies and talk about how freakin' cool the coloring is... even the graphics on the disc is freakin' awesome. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=otakulad>OtakuLad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Canadian <img src=http://contest.polykarbon.com/badge1.gif></span><br> <font color=#336699>(12/9/02 10:33:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2080.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.calgarymedia.com/asuka.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The Voices of a Distant Star</span><hr size=1> I haven't seen it, but the whole time issue reminds me of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://animeworld.com/reviews/gunbuster.html">Gunbuster</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. Sounds cool though! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=komikino>komikino</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(12/9/02 11:23:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2080.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://schleiferstudios.com/dan